dictionary.description: Whether decades pass, or even centuries, her love never fades. Having visited thousands of worlds and formed bonds with many of the people who inhabit them, the Goddess Tilith's heart is no doubt connected to many others regardless of distance. With a fearless disposition open to every type of person and every type of ideology, everyone is one and the same in her eyes. And even if evil threatens to rear its ugly head once again to destroy it all, it still will not be enough to stop her love for others.
dictionary.evolution: Could it be that I've grown even prettier than before? I didn't even know that was possible! Thank you so much for all your help!
dictionary.fusion:
The power to open the gates to people's hearts is not mine alone.
It's also yours because it's powered by my friendship with all of you!
dictionary.summon: Your favorite pretty goddess has arrived! Let's keep moving forward together!
